<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 9. Male genitalia of subgenus Bembidion Hydrium A B. levigatum (voucher DNA 1693, Virginia: Danville City Co., Danville) B B. levigatum (voucher DNA 2343, Texas: Bastrop Co., Colorado River near Utley) C B. mimbres (voucher DNA 2134, USA: New Mexico: Grant Co., Gila River, Billings Vista) D B. mimbres (voucher DNA 2135, USA: New Mexico: Grant Co., Gila River, Billings Vista). Scale bar: 0.1 mm." , "Figure 8. Adult males of subgenus Bembidion Hydrium A Bembidion levigatum (voucher V 100820, from USA: Utah: Grand Co., Moab, Colorado River, 1190 m, 38.5739 ° N, 109.5769 ° W) and B B. mimbres (a paratype from the type locality, voucher V 101458). Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/492373" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/492372" .

